sketch.compiler.ast.core.exprs

Class ExprArrayRange

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.FENode
      • sketch.compiler.ast.core.exprs.Expression
        • sketch.compiler.ast.core.exprs.ExprArrayRange

  • public class ExprArrayRange
extends Expression
    An array-range reference. A[0:2] means the first 3 elements of A, and A[4::2] means elements 4 and 5 of A. See Sketch language manual for more information.
    Author:
    liviu
